83rd OREGON LEGISLATIVE ASSEMBLY--2026 Regular Session
HOUSE AMENDMENTS TO
A-ENGROSSED SENATE BILL 1587
By COMMITTEE ON RULES
February 26
1 On page 1 of the printed A-engrossed bill, line 2, delete “declaring an emergency” and insert
2 “prescribing an effective date”.
3 In line 18, after “jurisdiction” insert “, or if the information is available to the general public
4 and is only disclosed under the same terms and conditions under which the information is available
5 to the general public”.
6 Delete line 19 and delete page 2 and insert:
7 “SECTION 2. This 2026 Act takes effect on the 91st day after the date on which the 2026
8 regular session of the Eighty-third Legislative Assembly adjourns sine die.”.
9
